survey.music_making: Clasically trained pianist from age 8-14, then moved over to guitar self taught from 15-35(current age).  Play mostly metal, have recorded one album with a band in the 2010's.  Also play keyboard, bass and drums.
survey.habit_change: Since the popularization of streaming platforms i have owned less and less physical media.  I collect classic vinyl but most of how i listen to music is thru streaming platforms.  I still like to listen to an "album" all at once rather than skip around or randomize songs.
